{"tid":1319042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話說頭先喺小巴聽到對廢老對話","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T07:07:07.000Z","uid":16039,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6d34c582a756e255c61ebd85b21b439d5d5683","tid":1319042,"uid":16039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"👨🏼&zwj;🦳廢老1    👨&zwj;🦳廢老2<br />\n<br />\n👨🏼&zwj;🦳:「啲警察好慘 維持治安但俾啲示威者掟磚 仲咬斷手指」<br />\n<br />\n👨&zwj;🦳: 「有大部份人都收左錢架嘛 」<br />\n<br />\n👨🏼&zwj;🦳:「成日話民主 宜家不知幾好 每個月有生果金 撘車兩蚊 得閒飲下茶幾好 爭取啲乜呀日日喺到搞搞震 我過多排都兩腳一伸反正乜都冇架啦 」<br />\n<br />\n👨&zwj;🦳:「咁你啲孫呢？」<br />\n<br />\n👨🏼&zwj;🦳:「佢地自己諗啦 總之唔關我事就得」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個社會就係有一班咁撚自私嘅廢老廢中 自己享受完香港最繁榮嘅時候唔再理下一代嘅生死  後生嗰時中意生仔就生 之後自己滿足左之後就唔撚理但家用照袋 養兒防老。如果屋企有啲咁嘅廢老唔撚好再養佢哋，就係呢班撚屌累死香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母 社會毒瘤</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2a217e74d368f9aad07ca4bc80adc7cc06f6da","tid":1319042,"uid":24317,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 佢唔應該睇到聽日既日出"},{"pid":"47c2b18e3e3749b4fd2eba63762b6cfcf8f827da","tid":1319042,"uid":16039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f2a217e74d368f9aad07ca4bc80adc7cc06f6da","tid":1319042,"uid":24317,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:32:51.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 佢唔應該睇到聽日既日出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:35:33.000Z","msg":"聽到勁撚嬲 所以廢老思想 TVB當然係成因<br />\n但更主要係因為佢地本身自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4440156de29c0dbca0d9895d9e5e0d4a31c7556c","tid":1319042,"uid":267969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:38:33.000Z","msg":"幾多歲度？<br />\n希望佢哋快啲死"},{"pid":"140807d5da9d0dc5e